title: .NET Platform Overview and Roadmap
description: This overview and roadmap session with Scott Hunter and Scott Hanselman will cover the present and future of .NET. We'll learn about new scenarios that .NET Core 3.0 will enable, supporting WinForms, WPF, ASP.NET Core, Azure, containers, IoT, massive scale and performance, and much more.
